# Netlify _redirects
# Drop this file in the root of your project (same level as index.html)
# Netlify reads it automatically on deploy

# Redirect bare domain → www (canonical)
https://joecoovermagic.com/*           https://www.joecoovermagic.com/:splat  301!

# Redirect Netlify subdomain → custom domain (once DNS is live)
https://joecoovermagic.netlify.app/*   https://www.joecoovermagic.com/:splat  301!

# Optional: redirect /book → /contact.html (nice short URL for business cards/ads)
/book   /contact.html   301
/book/  /contact.html   301
